gml_Object_obj_truechara_Step_0.gml_25: You really went through with it the entire way.
gml_Object_obj_truechara_Step_0.gml_28: I know you will have to go back eventually.
gml_Object_obj_truechara_Step_0.gml_29: Next time, I will get the coordinates right, an$3 **#$
gml_Object_obj_truechara_Step_0.gml_41: This must be why it all felt so familiar.
gml_Object_obj_truechara_Step_0.gml_42: Just what the hell are you?
gml_Object_obj_truechara_Step_0.gml_43: You can't be human. You can't be.
gml_Object_obj_truechara_Step_0.gml_44: Is it going to end the same as last time...?
gml_Object_obj_twm2_Collision_1576.gml_4: Trusting you was a major mistake.
gml_Object_obj_twm2_Collision_1576.gml_6: I know you can do that.
gml_Object_obj_twm2_Collision_1576.gml_8: WHAT THE HELL IS WRONG WITH YOU?
gml_Object_obj_twm2_Collision_1576.gml_9: Things will not go your way if you keep going.
gml_Object_obj_twm2_Collision_1576.gml_1: Even with what little power I have, I will make sure of that.
gml_Object_obj_twm_Collision_0.gml_4: Rather, what are you making Niko do?
gml_Object_obj_twm_Collision_0.gml_5: I saw this entire town evacuate due to a person of their description.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_8886: We meet again, sooner than expected.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_8887: I am not sure as to what happened.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_8888: The portal I created should have brought Niko home.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_8889: However, it seems... to have brought them to another location in your machine.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_8890: Needless to say, this was not supposed to happen.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_8891: I am trying to make a new one, but this world's code is very confusing.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_8892: What in the world is a 'GML'?
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_8893: I also seem to be only able to see a limited number of rooms in this world.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_8895: You seem to have a vast amount of control over this world.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_8896: Use that power wisely and keep Niko out of danger.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_9354: Bring Niko to it, it should only be a few meters away from there.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_9372: Why is Niko several thousand meters underground?
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_9373: I thought this place was located on the surface!
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_9375: I did not take altitude into consideration when creating the portal. It's on surface level.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_9376: You'll have to guide Niko to the surface. I'll try my best to help.
gml_Script_SCR_TEXT.gml_9377: And no, I can't just make another one.
